quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Mwari wenyu ndiMwari vamwechete (Allah). Asi avo vasingatendi muhupenyu hwemangwana, moyo yavo inoramba (kutenda muhumwechete hwaAllah), uye vanozvikudza"
  16,23,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoziva zvavanovanza nezvavanoburitsa. Zvirokwazvo, (Allah) havadi vanozvikudza"
  16,24,"Uye kana zvikanzi kwavari: “Chii chakadzikiswa naTenzi venyu (kuna Muhammad (SAW))?” Vanoti: “Ingano dzemadzitateguru!”"
  16,25,"Vachatakura mutoro wavo zvizere pazuva rekumutswa, uye nemutoro weavo vavakarunzira (vavakarasisa) vasina ruzivo. Zvirokwazvo, uipi ndeizvo zvavachatakura"